<Base title={`Fire Safety Services in $Stockton, $CA — Inspection, Installation & Compliance`} description={`Fire safety services for $Stockton, $CA commercial properties. Fire extinguisher inspection, fire alarm installation, sprinkler systems, kitchen suppression, and California Fire Code compliance. $Stockton Fire Department violation remediation and pre-inspection consulting.`} canonical={`https://firesafetysupplyhouse.com/fire-safety-services-$stockton-ca/`}>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-16"><div class="section">
    <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-400 mb-8"><a href="/" class="hover:text-gray-700 no-underline">Home</a><span>/</span><span class="text-gray-700">Fire Safety Services in Stockton, CA</span></nav>
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-brand mb-3">Serving Stockton, California & San Joaquin County</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-5 leading-tight">Fire Safety Services in Stockton, CA</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">Complete fire protection services for commercial properties in Stockton, California. Fire extinguisher inspection, fire alarm installation, sprinkler systems, kitchen suppression, and California Fire Code compliance consulting — performed by licensed professionals to keep your building compliant with Stockton Fire Department requirements and NFPA standards.</p>
