          <div><p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">Stockton Fire Department — Fire Prevention</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-600">22 E. Market Street, Stockton, CA 95202</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Phone: (209) 937-8250</p></div>
